Explanation_11: Action1: You  wrote review  review text:  "I got the Energy Micro 5.1 for my living room to balance my desire for better sound with my wife not wanting obtrusive audio gear cluttering the room. I am only using the front 3 speakers and sub woofer as my surrounds are in-ceiling. What can I say... audio clarity is excellent and having a separate center really helps with separating dialog from other sound effects. The speakers can put out a surprisingly high volume before experiencing any distortion and are complemented well by the small sub. As a bonus, they also look very good and sit nicely mounted on the wall, barely extending beyond my low-profile mounted LCD. I've mounted them using the VideoSecu MS40B4 WN3 (the ones with the 1/4" 20 thread) and they fit perfectly. Your satisfaction will probably depend somewhat on the room they are installed in but a little common sense is needed. These will sound weak in a 20'x20' greatroom but for a modest living room or TV area they are perfect." for item "Energy RC-Micro 5.1 Surround Speaker System (Black)" (with categories "Electronics")

Explanation_11: Action1: You  wrote review  review text:  "I got the Energy Micro 5.1 for my living room to balance my desire for better sound with my wife not wanting obtrusive audio gear cluttering the room. I am only using the front 3 speakers and sub woofer as my surrounds are in-ceiling. What can I say... audio clarity is excellent and having a separate center really helps with separating dialog from other sound effects. The speakers can put out a surprisingly high volume before experiencing any distortion and are complemented well by the small sub. As a bonus, they also look very good and sit nicely mounted on the wall, barely extending beyond my low-profile mounted LCD. I've mounted them using the VideoSecu MS40B4 WN3 (the ones with the 1/4" 20 thread) and they fit perfectly. Your satisfaction will probably depend somewhat on the room they are installed in but a little common sense is needed. These will sound weak in a 20'x20' greatroom but for a modest living room or TV area they are perfect." for item "Energy RC-Micro 5.1 Surround Speaker System (Black)" (with categories "Electronics")
